{
  "texts": [
    "In contrast, DEXs prioritize global accessibility and anonymity, bypassing Know Your Customer (KYC) and Anti-Money Laundering (AML) regulations (Aspris et al., 2021).",
    "This approach can be seen as a double-edged sword.",
    "On the one hand, it opens the door to a wider range of listings and cross-border trading opportunities (Dewey & Newbold, 2023).",
    "On the other hand, it raises concerns about potential money laundering and illicit financial activities (Dai, 2020).",
    "The increased anonymity of DEXs may make them an attractive platform for individuals seeking to engage in these activities."
  ]
}